title: Blood On The Dance Floor - Bad Blood (2013)
description:
This is iTunes' bonus edition of Blood on the Dance Floor's Bad Blood album in .m4a format*, free of charge!

Tracklisting:
1. Unchained
2. I Refuse To SInk
3. Bad Blood
4. Always & Forever
5. Fake Is The New Trend
6. Damaged
7. Bohemyth
8. Divided We Fall
9. Crucified By Your Lies
10. Something Grimm
11. Redeemer
12. Mourning Star
13. Everyone Dies Alone
14. Sick Sad World (Bonus Track)
15. Revenge Will Have Its Day (Bonus Track)

*Apart from the track "Unchained", which was mislabeled and in fact a duplicate of "Reedemer" in the original, so I replaced it with the correct song, albeit in .mp3 format.
